1.title: Arrival (Pilot)

episode of.title: On the Wings of Love (TV Series 2015–2016)

1.plot: Young Leah Olivar recounts her childhood memories before the departure of her mother going to San Francisco up to the receiving the news of her mother's demise. Leah who is now 22 years old went to the US Embassy for a visa interview they needed for her and choir mates to compete in San Francisco. While at San Francisco, Leah came across Clark Medina accidentally.
